---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | A Quiet Space" description="A Quiet Space was created from a simple observation: modern life constantly encourages people to accumulate more. We want to build a brand that encourages people to be more intentional about what they carry.">
  <div class="about-wrapper">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1 class="brand-title sentient-heading">A Quiet Space</h1>
      <span class="brand-tagline satoshi-text">carry what matters</span>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title sentient-heading">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          A Quiet Space is a lifestyle brand and design studio based in Jakarta, Indonesia. We specialize in producing premium carrying systems and functional everyday goods. Our approach combines high-utility product design with structured narrative themes, creating objects that serve daily tasks while carrying a quiet, intentional meaning.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title sentient-heading">2. Why A Quiet Space Exists</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          Modern life encourages the continuous accumulation of material goods, digital noise, and constant distraction. This environment often leads to feeling overwhelmed by clutter. A Quiet Space was created to address this problem, offering a minimal counter-perspective that favors simplicity, intentional design, and the reduction of material excess.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title sentient-heading">3. The Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          Our brand is built on three core philosophical pillars:
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          <strong>Carry What Matters:</strong> A design guideline and lifestyle practice that prompts individuals to evaluate what they bring with them, both physically in their bags and mentally in their daily lives.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          <strong>Intentional Ownership:</strong> The practice of selecting objects deliberately based on utility, durability, and character, rather than following short-lived consumption trends.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          <strong>Enoughness:</strong> The recognition of physical limits and the appreciation of what is sufficient. We believe utility is maximized when excess is eliminated.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title sentient-heading">4. The State of Enough (SOE)</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          "The State of Enough" (SOE) represents the first chapter and product release of A Quiet Space. It serves as a study in containment. By focusing on essential carrying needs, the products in this chapter—beginning with the SOE Bag 1—are built to house only daily essentials, encouraging users to define their personal boundary of enoughness and live within it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-title sentient-heading">5. The AQS Universe</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          A Quiet Space operates as a narrative-driven project where products are released in thematic chapters rather than standard seasonal fashion cycles. Future chapters will explore themes such as patience, focus, quietness, and resilience. Each theme is explored through curated design variations, written reflections, and physical objects, forming a cohesive universe of stories.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section final-section">
        <h2 class="section-title sentient-heading">6. Closing</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          A Quiet Space designs objects for the quiet space between excess and necessity. We build carrying systems that support daily movement while reminding us to carry only what matters.
        </p>
        <div class="closing-brand satoshi-text">
          carry what matters
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-wrapper {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 8rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .sentient-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .satoshi-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }

  .brand-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xxl);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .brand-tagline {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4.5rem;
  }

  .about-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-top: -0.25rem;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .closing-brand {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-wrapper {
      padding: 4rem 1.25rem 6rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .about-header {
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .about-content {
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }

    .about-text {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
